con:config.con:query: SELECT BVCBNO CABIN_NUMBER, ABSDDT, ABSHIP, AB.ABPAID PAX_ID, BVBKID BOOKING_ID, BVDEMA, ABPLNM LAST_NAME, ABPFNM FIRST_NAME FROM RZBKVD BV INNER JOIN RZPITD AB ON BVBKID = ABBKID AND BVSHIP = ABSHIP AND ABSDDT = BVSDDT WHERE BVBKID = 85308;
